 De Glicerila), Tocopheryl Acetate (Acetato De Dextroalfatocoferol), Phytosteryl Oleate (Oleato De Fitosterila), Ci 77499 (Óxido De Ferro Preto), Parfum (Fragrância), Tin Oxide (Óxido De Estanho), Phytosterols (Fitosteróis), Bht (Butil-Hidroxitolueno)."]},"__typename":"SpecificationGroupProperty"},"Product:kit-paleta-de-sombras-power-glow-iluminador-em-bastao-bronze-oceane-edition-k1094.specificationGroups.3.specifications.6":{"name":"Selos","originalName":"Selos","values":{"type":"json","json":["Vegano","Cruelty Free"]},"__typename":"SpecificationGroupProperty"},"Product:kit-paleta-de-sombras-power-glow-iluminador-em-bastao-bronze-oceane-edition-k1094.specificationGroups.3.specifications.7":{"name":"Parcerias","originalName":"Parcerias","values":{"type":"json","json":["Océane Edition"]},"__typename":"SpecificationGroupProperty"},"Product:kit-paleta-de-sombras-power-glow-iluminador-em-bastao-bronze-oceane-edition-k1094.specificationGroups.3.specifications.8":{"name":"sellerId","originalName":"sellerId","values":{"type":"json","json":["1"]},"__typename":"SpecificationGroupProperty"},"$Product:kit-paleta-de-sombras-power-glow-iluminador-em-bastao-bronze-oceane-edition-k1094.skuSpecifications.0.field":{"name":"PROMOCAO","originalName":"PROMOCAO","__typename":"SKUSpecificationField"},"Product:kit-paleta-de-sombras-power-glow-iluminador-em-bastao-bronze-oceane-edition-k1094.skuSpecifications.0":{"field":{"type":"id","generated":true,"id":"$Product:kit-paleta-de-sombras-power-glow-iluminador-em-bastao-bronze-oceane-edition-k1094.skuSpecifications.0.field","typename":"SKUSpecificationField"},"values":[{"type":"id","generated":true,"id":"Product:kit-paleta-de-sombras-power-glow-iluminador-em-bastao-bronze-oceane-edition-k1094.skuSpecifications.0.values.0","typename":"SKUSpecificationValue"}],"__typename":"SkuSpecification"},"Product:kit-paleta-de-sombras-power-glow-iluminador-em-bastao-bronze-oceane-edition-k1094.skuSpecifications.0.values.0":{"name":"Não","originalName":"N